The youngster was taken to the Royal Alexandra Children's Hospital to undergo treatment.

Police said the dog was off the lead with two similar dogs - two were black and one was white. 

They were with a man described as being in his 50s, with purple hair and a brown moustache.

Anyone with information is asked to contact police. 

